sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Customer
    participant V as Vendor POS
    participant LB as Logistics Bridge
    participant R as Toofan or Rider
    participant API as Shop API
    participant GW as WhatsApp Gateway
    participant WA as WhatsApp
    participant DB as Supabase

    Note over C,DB: After customer places order — status is CONFIRMED

    V->>API: PATCH status PROCESSING (invoice created)
    API->>DB: Update order to PROCESSING
    API->>LB: POST /api/dispatch-delivery fire-and-forget
    LB->>R: Assign rider to order

    Note over R,DB: Rider arrives at vendor and picks up package

    R->>LB: POST /webhooks/toofan event PICKED_UP orderId
    LB->>DB: UPDATE orders SET status DISPATCHED
    DB->>DB: log_order_status_change trigger

    Note over R,DB: Rider delivers package to customer

    R->>LB: POST /webhooks/toofan event DELIVERED orderId
    LB->>DB: UPDATE orders SET status DELIVERED
    LB->>DB: Read payment_token buyer_whatsapp grand_total order_no
    LB->>GW: POST /api/send-payment-link

    GW->>WA: Your order has been delivered. Pay here slash pay slash orderId question token equals ...
    WA->>C: WhatsApp notification with payment link

    Note over C,WA: Customer opens link — no login required, token is the credential

    C->>API: GET /api/shop/pay/orderId?token=...
    API->>DB: Validate token + expiry + status DELIVERED
    API-->>C: order_no, grand_total, seller_name

    C->>C: Select payment screenshot from gallery or camera

    C->>API: POST /api/shop/pay/orderId with token imageBase64 mimeType
    API->>API: verifyPaymentImage from lib/vision/server-payment-ocr.js
    API->>DB: INSERT payment_attempts (attempt tracking, max 3)

    alt OCR Verified
        API->>DB: UPDATE orders SET status COMPLETED payment_token null payment_ref referenceNo completed_at NOW payment_method detected
        API->>GW: POST /api/send-receipt fire-and-forget
        GW->>WA: Receipt to customer
        API-->>C: success true order_no referenceNo
        C->>C: Confirmation screen
    else OCR Failed attempts less than 3
        API-->>C: verified false reason attemptsLeft
        C->>C: Retry button
    else Max 3 attempts reached
        API-->>C: verified false Max attempts reached
        C->>C: Contact store message
    end

    Note over V,API: Vendor fallback path
    Note over V,API: If Toofan not yet live, vendor can PATCH DISPATCHED then DELIVERED manually
    Note over V,API: On DELIVERED the API auto-sends the payment link — same result
